Here are all the winners: Ferrari 3.9-litre biturbo V8 (Ferrari 488 GTB/Spider) Porsche 3-litre six-cylinder turbo (Porsche 911 Carrera, 911 Carrera 4, 911 Carrera S, 911 Carrera 4S, Carrera GTS) BMW 1.5-litre three-cylinder electric-gasoline hybrid (BMW i8) Audi 2.5-litre five-cylinder turbo (Audi RS3, TT RS) Ford 999cc three-cylinder turbo (Ford Fiesta, B-Max, Focus, C-Max, Grand C-Max, Mondeo, EcoSport) Tesla full-electric powertrain (Tesla Model S, Model X) PSA Peugeot Citroen 1.2-litre three-cylinder turbo (Peugeot 208, 308, 2008, 3008, 5008, Citroen C3, C3 Picasso, C4, C4 Cactus, C4 Picasso / Grand Picasso, DS3, DS4) Porsche 2-litre turbo (Porsche 718 Boxster, 718 Cayman) Ferrari 6.3-litre V12 (Ferrari F12, F12 tdf)</li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li> To view all the results, go to the International Engine of the Year website.